name: Luces
description:
Cuba is an island of lights and shadows.
As Cubans, we struggle to see the light more than the shadows, although sometimes it is very difficult.
The flag in this image represents that light, that breath of life, of color that stands out above the shadows of a city, of a wall hit by the sea.

5/5  Editions are the quantity of points of the flag star and stripes.
Size: 3404x2554px
